300aa12e5","tid":334394,"uid":87511,"like":65,"dislike":1,"score":64,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T01:52:20.000Z","msg":"講起做雞呢個話題<br />\n就算大家都係做雞,香港女人做雞個格都寧舍衰過人<br />\n<br />\n支那女人做雞都會係敬業樂業<br />\n你畀得起錢,就會畀返相應嘅服務你<br />\n<br />\n香港嗰啲唔撚係<br />\n早輪個乜鳩PTGF之亂真係睇到我眼都突<br />\n淨係接靚仔/有錢仔生意<br />\n對其他男顧客直頭不屑一顧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最令我睇唔過眼係佢哋明明有人真係賣閪求榮<br />\n人哋稱呼佢哋做雞,佢哋又話人唔尊重佢哋<br />\n<br />\n點解佢哋覺得人哋叫佢哋做雞係唔尊重? 其實佢哋先係真正睇唔起性工作者嘅人<br />\n結論 <span style=\"color: red;\">香港女人做雞都麻鳩煩過人 要求多多不突止,仲要做雞又要拎貞節牌坊</span>"},{"pid":"9f9fe1dbf8cf0ad3bc27a35eb6bca733d8c5c3ad","tid":334394,"uid":20241,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T02:19:10.000Z","msg":"the best is yet to come"},{"pid":"d03db06076855b13e8782b2fec4a4f7923931834","tid":334394,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T02:21:10.000Z","msg":"台灣呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f7fab086a1de70ae67a6cb4494abc933db51c81","tid":334394,"uid":80411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T02:27:15.000Z","msg":"港女：The best is yet to come"},{"pid":"08add571f300620ca4c0fc2af56b534d22e40b60","tid":334394,"uid":6604,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T02:28:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>台灣呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/1510000/1511469/yauf20150729055_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F1510000%2F1511469%2Fyauf20150729055_1024.jpg&h=4871c8f2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ecb6eaf6c019e072849c6d78ccb55f941caadf12","tid":334394,"uid":8681,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T02:29:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港女：The best is yet to come</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\